<p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" data-attachment-id="237887" data-permalink="https://lithub.com/morgan-talty-on-writing-a-native-american-novel-that-subverts-expectations/fire-exit/" data-orig-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/fire-exit.jpeg" data-orig-size="323,500" data-comments-opened="1" data-image-meta="{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;0&quot;}" data-image-title="fire exit" data-image-description="" data-image-caption="" data-medium-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/fire-exit-194x300.jpeg" data-large-file="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/fire-exit.jpeg" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-237887" src="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/fire-exit-194x300.jpeg" alt="" width="194" height="300" srcset="https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/fire-exit-194x300.jpeg 194w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/fire-exit-39x60.jpeg 39w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/fire-exit-32x50.jpeg 32w, https://s26162.pcdn.co/wp-content/uploads/2024/05/fire-exit.jpeg 323w" sizes="(max-width: 194px) 100vw, 194px" /></p>
